	- token.mintTokens(cofounditAddress,cofounditReward) (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol)
	State variables written after the call(s):

Reentrancy in MusiconomiCrowdsale.claimCoreTeamsTokens (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#338-349):

	- devReward = maxTokenSupply - token.totalSupply() (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#340)
	- token.mintTokens(_to,devReward) (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#347-348)

Reentrancy in MusiconomiCrowdsale.processTransaction (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#210-240):

	- token.mintTokens(_contributor,tokenAmount) (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#234)

MusiconomiCrowdsale.salvageTokensFromContract (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#264-271) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20Token(_tokenAddress).transfer(_to,_amount) (/unique_chucks/17/0x68223df196b3c46b7eb30a154dc79aa0a9d7907a.sol#267-271)
